---
// Features component for electrician website
---

<section class="bg-[#1a1a1a] py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Experienced Team -->
      <div class="border border-[#F4C430] rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-4 items-stretch">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160562-40aa08e78837?w=200&h=150&fit=crop&q=80" 
            alt="Experienced Team" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Experienced Team</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300" style="font-size: 14px;">
            Backed by an experienced team, we provide expertise and guidance to ensure optimal selection and utilization.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Modern Equipment -->
      <div class="border border-[#F4C430] rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-4 items-stretch">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905251918-48416bd8575a?w=200&h=150&fit=crop&q=80" 
            alt="Modern Equipment" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Modern Equipment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300" style="font-size: 14px;">
            Equipped with state-of-the-art technology and modern machinery, we streamline processes to ensure efficiency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Smart Methods -->
      <div class="border border-[#F4C430] rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-4 items-stretch">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092918056-0c4c3acd3789?w=200&h=150&fit=crop&q=80" 
            alt="Smart Methods" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Smart Methods</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300" style="font-size: 14px;">
            Employing smart methodologies, we optimize resource utilization and minimize waste throughout our production processes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
